// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1574 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: bdfbc9d3-a6ca-541c-9424-f031c7aeaaae

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
